title: Orion Taraban
description: Presented by Orion Taraban, Psy.D., PsycHacks provides viewers with a brief, thought-provoking video twice a week on a variety of psychological topics, inspired by his clinical practice. The intention is for the core idea contained within each video to inspire viewers to see something about themselves or their world in a slightly different light. The ultimate mission of the channel is to reduce the amount of unnecessary suffering in the world.
